{"name":"elaca-3-4-form-ResponseGroupChecklistforInformationalWriting","pages":[{"engine":{"module":"engines/form","payload":{"fieldsets":[{"content":"<h1>Response Group Checklist for Informational Writing<br></h1><div class='instructions instructions-callout'><p>Everyone in your Response Group will get a turn to read his or her piece aloud, mark off the checklist, and write down suggestions for revision. To begin, one student in the Response Group should read his or her piece aloud while the other members of the group listen.  After reading, the author should hold the checklist and then ask the other members of the Response Group to respond to each element on the checklist.  The author should write down the suggested revisions. Then it’s the next person’s turn to read aloud. </p></div><div class='scrollable-table-top'><table><thead><tr><th style='width:32%;height:100px;'><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Questions</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p></th><th style='width:15%;height:100px;'><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Yes</p></th><th style='width:15%;height:100px;'><p style=\"text-align: center;\">No</p></th><th style='width:38%;height:100px;'><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Revision Notes</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p></th></tr></thead></table></div><div class='scrollable-table-bottom'><table><tbody><tr><td style='width:32%;height:100px;'><p>Does your piece introduce the topic clearly and engage the reader?</p></td><td style='width:15%;height:100px;'>{{2-2}}</td><td style='width:15%;height:100px;'>{{2-3}}</td><td style='width:38%;height:100px;'>{{2-4}}</td></tr><tr><td style='width:32%;height:100px;'><p>Does your piece organize related information in paragraphs and/or sections?</p></td><td style='width:15%;height:100px;'>{{3-2}}</td><td style='width:15%;height:100px;'>{{3-3}}</td><td style='width:38%;height:100px;'>{{3-4}}</td></tr><tr><td style='width:32%;height:100px;'><p>Does your piece develop the topic with facts, definitions, details, quotations, or other information and examples?</p></td><td style='width:15%;height:100px;'>{{4-2}}</td><td style='width:15%;height:100px;'>{{4-3}}</td><td style='width:38%;height:100px;'>{{4-4}}</td></tr><tr><td style='width:32%;height:100px;'><p>Does your piece connect ideas within categories with appropriate words and phrases?</p></td><td style='width:15%;height:100px;'>{{5-2}}</td><td style='width:15%;height:100px;'>{{5-3}}</td><td style='width:38%;height:100px;'>{{5-4}}</td></tr></tbody></table></div>","className":"subject-ELA left-header top-header","fields":{"2-2":{"name":"2-2","attr":{"name":"2","type":"radio","value":"2"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"2-3":{"name":"2-3","attr":{"name":"2","type":"radio","value":"3"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"2-4":{"name":"2-4","attr":{"class":"contenteditable","name":"2-4"},"tagName":"textarea"},"3-2":{"name":"3-2","attr":{"name":"3","type":"radio","value":"2"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"3-3":{"name":"3-3","attr":{"name":"3","type":"radio","value":"3"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"3-4":{"name":"3-4","attr":{"class":"contenteditable","name":"3-4"},"tagName":"textarea"},"4-2":{"name":"4-2","attr":{"name":"4","type":"radio","value":"2"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"4-3":{"name":"4-3","attr":{"name":"4","type":"radio","value":"3"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"4-4":{"name":"4-4","attr":{"class":"contenteditable","name":"4-4"},"tagName":"textarea"},"5-2":{"name":"5-2","attr":{"name":"5","type":"radio","value":"2"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"5-3":{"name":"5-3","attr":{"name":"5","type":"radio","value":"3"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"5-4":{"name":"5-4","attr":{"class":"contenteditable","name":"5-4"},"tagName":"textarea"}},"rowAddable":false}]}}}],"version":"2015-02-04T17:50:55.646Z"}